      "content": "thanks but i just tried that with n=10^7 and it's still super slow... it's still doing way too many iterations for the big test cases. the grader is really strict on the time limit, like it needs it to be almost instant for n=10^7. is there any way to make it run way faster? even if it's just for the massive inputs?",
      "source": "evaluator"
